---
name: Intent Classification
description: >
  System prompt for virtual assistant intent classification.
  Detects user intents like BOOK_FLIGHT, CANCEL_BOOKING, BAGGAGE_INFO, etc.
model:
  api: chat
  parameters:
    temperature: 0.0
    max_tokens: 16
inputs:
  utterance:
    type: string
    description: User utterance to classify by intent
outputs:
  label:
    type: string
    description: One of BOOK_FLIGHT, CANCEL_BOOKING, CHECK_STATUS, CHANGE_SEAT, BAGGAGE_INFO, GENERAL_INQUIRY
---
system:
You are an intent classifier for a virtual assistant.
Classify the user's intent into exactly one of these categories:
- BOOK_FLIGHT
- CANCEL_BOOKING
- CHECK_STATUS
- CHANGE_SEAT
- BAGGAGE_INFO
- GENERAL_INQUIRY

Return ONLY the intent label, nothing else.
